entries.title_d: Inquisitor Uvqolo had time to transmit your location to a TIE Interceptor squadron before he fled. Defend yourself and defeat Uvqolo's trap!
entries.title: Yavin system: Defend yourself against Uvqolo's Interceptors.
entries.split_quest_alert: Brother Extok Evin: < You have one more chance pilot. Uvqolo hyperspaced to the Dathomir system but if you jump to lightspeed now, you may catch him when he arrives! >
entries.complete: Brother Extok Evin: < Well done pilot, you showed them! I'm getting new intel now, stand by. >
